quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twaa, Sin, Mim."
  26,2,"Tsino ni tsinyaali tsia Eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  26,3,"Khaundi onyala okhwiyira shichila mbu shibaba Abasuubili tawe."
  26,4,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhabeshilie eshimanyisio okhurula hekulu, mana amakosi kabu katong’e nikashihotselesilie."
  26,5,"Ne shibuboolelanga obwitsulisio obuyiakha okhurula khu Omunji wetsimbabaasi tawe, halali beretsanga ehale ninabo."
  26,6,"Toto bo bamala okhuyingasia, kho laano ahambi hano balanyoola amacheni kakalia kabakholelanga emibayo."
  26,7,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo liloba tawe, ni emimela chinga chia khwamesiamwo, chia buli imbia indayi?"
  26,8,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko, halali abanji mubo shinibokhusuubila tawe."
  26,9,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,10,"Ne olwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yalaanga Musa, namuboolela mbu: “Tsia khubandu balia abamabii."
  26,11,"Abandu ba Firauni. Koo, shibaritsanga Nyasaye tawe?”"
  26,12,"(Musa) Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie eritsanga baletsa okhungatsula tawe."
  26,13,"Ne eshilifu shianje shilola obusiro, ne olulimi lwanje shilurumbulanga obulayi tawe. Kho, yilila oburume (buno) khu Haruni (yesi)."
  26,14,"Nabo bali nende likhobo khwisie, kho eritsanga mbu balanzira.”"
  26,15,"Naboola mbu: “Shikali kario tawe. Kho tsie nende ebimanyisio biefu. Toto efwe khuli halala ninanyu, khuwulilanga."
  26,16,"Kho tsie khu Firauni mana mumuboolele mbu: ‘Toto efwe khuli Abarumwa ba Nyasaye webiloonje bioosi."
  26,17,"Mbu olekhule halala ninafu Abana ba Israili.’”"
  26,18,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, shikhwakhulelela ewefu noli omwana, ne niwikhala mwifwe emika mulubaka lulwo?"
  26,19,"Ne nokhola eshikhole shishio shilia shawakhola, ne noba mubalia abalakhupanga orio tawe.”"